msgctxt "120_Entrepreneur"
msgid "Say, aren't you－you wouldn't happen to be...?"
msgstr "Un momento... ¿No es usted...? No me diga que es..."

msgctxt "132_Call Girl"
msgid "If you're going to pester everyone about the arena,\\r\n"\n"I'm going to sign you up for a cage match..."
msgstr "Si vas a seguir jodiendo a todos con lo de la arena,\\r te apunto para un combate en jaula..."

msgctxt "144_Call Girl"
msgid "Pardon him. He just can't seem to hold his liquor."
msgstr "Perdónalo, es que no aguanta ni una copa."

